title: Converse Cons congratulates Ben Raemers on turning Pro.
description:
Converse CONS congratulates Ben Raemers on joining the ranks of professional skateboarding. In celebration, Ben gave us a look into his life and took us around some of his favourite old parks and street spots in and around London, England. 

Filmed and edited by Dan Magee
Music by Joel Curtis
